<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_05_IH_0007</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_05.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_ih_0007">
			<section class="title type2">
				<i class="icon_creative" lang="y"><span>창</span><span>의</span></i>
				<h2 data-head="7_deep_green" class="is_star2" lang="y">
					수 카드 8장 중 4장을 골라 한 번씩만 사용하여 비례식을 세우고, 비례식을 세운 방법을 써 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center align_start">
					<div class="l_left">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_05_IH/0007_bg.png" alt="" />
							<img
								src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_05_IH/0007_cards.png"
								class="cards_img"
								alt=""
							/>
							<div class="input_area">
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field></math-field>
									<div class="example_box">
										<p>6</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								:
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field></math-field>
									<div class="example_box">
										<p>9</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								=
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field></math-field>
									<div class="example_box">
										<p>2</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								:
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field></math-field>
									<div class="example_box">
										<p>3</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="l_right">
						<span class="label_gray" lang="y"> 방법 </span>
						<div class="input_wrap">
							<math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
							<div class="example_box">
								<p lang="y">6×3=18, 9×2=18이므로 6과 3이 외항, 9와 2가 내항인 비례식을 세웠습니다.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>두 수의 곱이 같은 수 카드를 찾아서 외항과 내항에 각각 놓아 비례식을 세웁니다.</p>
								<p>여러 가지 비례식을 세울 수 있습니다.</p>
								<p>2 : 3=4 : 6, 2 : 4=8 : 16, 3 : 4=9 : 12</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">제출</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
